      "Text": "Security update for openexr",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for openexr fixes the following issues:\n\n- CVE-2021-3474: Undefined-shift in Imf_2_5::FastHufDecoder::FastHufDecoder (bsc#1184174)\n- CVE-2021-3475: Integer-overflow in Imf_2_5::calculateNumTiles (bsc#1184173)\n- CVE-2021-3476: Undefined-shift in Imf_2_5::unpack14 (bsc#1184172)\n\nThis update was imported from the SUSE:SLE-15:Update update project.",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
